Maintainer: Yilin Ning <ningyilinnyl@gmail.com>
Description: A lightweight toolkit to evaluate and visualize bias in AI 
    prediction models. seeBias supports comprehensive subgroup assessments with 
    respect to model classification performance, calibration, and beyond, 
    integrates fairness metrics with model performance, and offers customizable 
    visualizations to facilitate transparent reporting.
